 
<p>
*Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe documents
the <a href="https://www.cnn.com/europe/live-news/russia-ukraine-war-news-07-14-22/h_c0aae7af379352e9ed57608044509206">discovery
of torture chambers</a> &hellip; in Bucha.*
<p>
The report also asserts that the <a href="/glossary.html#putinforces">Putin forces</a> used Ukrainian civilians
as human shields.

 